---
title: Tomato Basil Bisque with Grilled Cheese Croutons and Balsamic Greens
description: There’s nothing better than a grilled cheese sandwich
dipped in warm tomato soup—especially when it’s
homemade! Why not cut to the chase and put your grilled
cheese directly in the soup? Total game changer.
